text: Amblymora marmorata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Amblymora marmorata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1939
title: Amblymora marmorata
